# total movies per year between 2010 and 2020
dbGetQuery(db, "SELECT * FROM movie_info 
           WHERE Release_Year
           BETWEEN 2010 AND 2020
           ORDER BY Release_Year") %>%
  group_by(Release_Year) %>% summarize(total=n()) %>% ggplot(aes(x= Release_Year, y = total)) +
  geom_bar(aes(fill = Release_Year), stat = "identity")

Q5

#choose top 25 to visualize
dbGetQuery(db, "SELECT d.Director_Name, SUM(m.Gross) AS 'Total_Gross'
FROM director_info d
JOIN movie_info m
ON d.Director_ID=m.Director_ID
WHERE Gross != 'NA'
GROUP BY d.Director_Name
ORDER BY Total_Gross DESC
LIMIT 25") %>% 
  mutate(Director_Name = fct_reorder(as.factor(Director_Name), Total_Gross, .desc = FALSE)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Director_Name, y = Total_Gross, fill=Director_Name)) + geom_bar(stat="identity") + coord_flip() +  scale_y_continuous(labels=scales::dollar) +
  labs(x= "Director", y="Total Gross")

# check if director name found
verifyDirector <- function(name) {
  df.name <- dbGetQuery(db, "SELECT Director_Name FROM director_info")
  name.list <- as.vector(df.name$Director)
  if (name %in% name.list) {
    print("name found")
  } else {
    print("name not found")
  }
}
verifyDirector("Frank Darabont")
## [1] "name found"
verifyDirector("Zunqiu Wang")
## [1] "name not found"
